ave the same number, 9.3.1, but are in different locations)</p> <p class=\"Paragraph\">With non-volitional verbs, ergative constructions are identical to those using volitional verbs: the subject is in the ergative case, while the object is in the absolutive.</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཚེ་རིང་གིས་རྟ་མཐོང་པ་རེད།</span> “Tsering saw the horse.”</li> </ul>","title":""}]}
